                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The electronic FOIA Library contains information that is made available on a routine basis to the public. It also features documents that are frequently requested under the FOIA. This collection of online documents continues to grow as records in which the public expresses an interest are added.</Paragraph>
